t></a>\n                    </td>\n                    <td bgcolor=\"#003399\"><img alt=\" \" width=\"2\" height=\"2\" src=\"/icons/spacer.gif\"></td>\n                  </tr>\n                  <tr>\n                    <td bgcolor=\"#DBDBDB\"><img alt=\" \" width=\"2\" height=\"2\" src=\"/icons/spacer.gif\"></td>\n                    <td bgcolor=\"#DBDBDB\" colspan=\"2\">\n                      <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n                        <tbody><tr>\n                          <td align=\"center\" valign=\"bottom\"><input type=\"submit\" style=\"text-decoration:none;font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica;font-size:10px;font-weight:bold;color:#000000;background:#FFFFFF;\" value=\"Go\"></td>\n                          <th align=\"left\" colspan=\"2\"><font size=\"-2\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\" color=\"#000000\"><label for=\"qsintdefsauthor1\">Author:</label><br></font> <input type=\"text\" name=\"author1\" id=\"qsintdefsauthor1\" size=\"9\" maxlength=\"80\" value=\"\" style=\"font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica;font-size:10px;\"></th>\n                          <th align=\"left\" colspan=\"3\"><font size=\"-2\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\" color=\"#000000\"><label for=\"qsintdefsfulltext\">Keyword(s):</label><br></font> <input type=\"text\" name=\"fulltext\" id=\"qsintdefsfulltext\" size=\"16\" maxlength=\"80\" value=\"\" style=\"font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica;font-size:10px;\"></th>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr>\n                          <th><font size=\"-2\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\" color=\"#000000\"><label for=\"qsintdefspubdate_year\">Year:</label>&nbsp;</font></th>\n                          <td><input type=\"text\" name=\"pubdate_year\" id=\"qsintdefspubdate_year\" size=\"4\" maxlength=\"4\" value=\"\" style=\"font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica;font-size:10px;\"></td>\n                          <th align=\"right\"><font size=\"-2\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\" color=\"#000000\"><label for=\"qsintdefsvolume\">Vol:</label>&nbsp;</font></th>\n                          <td><input type=\"text\" name=\"volume\" id=\"qsintdefsvolume\" size=\"4\" maxlength=\"10\" value=\"\" style=\"font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica;font-size:10px;\"></td>\n                          <th><font size=\"-2\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica,sans-serif\" color=\"#000000\"><label for=\"qsintdefsfirstpage\">Page:</label>&nbsp;</font></th>\n                          <td><input type=\"text\" name=\"firstpage\" id=\"qsintdefsfirstpage\" size=\"4\" maxlength=\"10\" value=\"\" style=\"font-family:verdana,arial,helvetica;font-size:10px;\"></td>\n                        </tr>\n                      </tbody></table>\n                    </td>\n                    <td bgcolor=\"#DBDBDB\"><img alt=\" \" width=\"2\" height=\"2\" src=\"/icons/spacer.gif\"></td>\n                  </tr>\n                </tbody></table>\n              </form>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody></table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td colspan=\"3\">\n        <img alt=\" \" width=\"2\" height=\"2\" src=\"/icons/spacer.gif\"><br>\n        <font size=\"-2\" face=\"verdana,arial,helvetica\"></font>\n        <hr align=\"left\" size=\"1\" color=\"#000000\" noshade=\"\">\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table>\n  <h2>About International Journal of Systematic and Evolutionary Microbiology (IJSEM)</h2>\n  <h3>ISSNs: Print 1466-5026; Online 1466-5034</h3>\n  <h3>Official publication of the International Committee on Systematics of Prokaryotes and the Bacteriology and Applied Microbiology Division of the International Union of Microbiological Societies</h3>\n  <hr>\n  <p><i>International Journal of Systematic and Evolutionary Microbiology</i> (IJSEM), formerly <i>International Journal of Systematic Bacteriology</i> (IJSB), is the official journal of record for novel prokaryotic taxa. Now in its 60th year (before 1966 it was known as the <i>International Bulletin of Bacteriological Nomenclature and Taxonomy</i>), the journal is the cornerstone of the dynamic field of microbial systematics.</p>\n  <p>IJSEM publishes papers dealing with all phases of the systematics of prokaryotes, yeasts and yeast-like organisms, including taxonomy, nomenclature, identification, phylogeny, evolution, biodiversity, characterization and culture preservation. Its scope covers phylogenetic and evolutionary aspects of all micro-organisms, including the protists such as protozoa and algae, and it also publishes molecular environmental papers with a strong systematics content. Its international <a href=\"/ijs/misc/edboard.shtml\">Editorial Board</a> ensures the highest standards of peer review.</p>\n  <p>IJSEM is published by the (SGM), a learned society that promotes microbiology at all levels.</p>\n  <table width=\"60%\" border=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"4\" bgcolor=\"#FF9933\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td><b>: 2.113</b><br>\n      <br>\n      Ranked <b>15th</b> highest research journal in microbiology by the (<b>0.02126</b>).</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table>\n  <hr>\n  <h3>IJSEM features:</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Descriptions of the majority of all new prokaryotic and yeast species</li>\n    <li>\n      <a href=\"#VL\">Validation Lists</a> - to validate officially the publication of names of prokaryotes not published in the IJSB/IJSEM\n    </li>\n    <li>Opinions of the Judicial Commission of the</li>\n    <li>Minutes of subcommittees</li>\n    <li>Over 3000 pages per annual volume</li>\n    <li>Different cover picture for each issue</li>\n  </ul>\n  <h3>Benefits to authors:</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Excellent editorial standards</li>\n    <li>Online submission and peer review</li>\n    <li>Excellent reproduction of figures</li>\n    <li>No page charges</li>\n    <li>Supplementary data facility in IJSEM Online</li>\n    <li>Authors receive 25 <b>free</b> offprints of their paper</li>\n  </ul>\n  <ul>\n    <li>\n      <a href=\"/ijs/misc/self_archiving.dtl\">Self-archiving</a>. Details of the SGM policy on author self-archiving\n    </li>\n    <li>\n      <a href=\"/ijs/misc/open_option.dtl\">Paid immediate open access</a>. Details of the SGM Open Option scheme that allows immediate open access to articles\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n  <hr>\n  <a name=\"subs\" id=\"subs\"></a>\n  <h3>Submission of papers</h3>\n  <p>Papers for publication must be submitted using our <a href=\"/ijs/misc/subonline.shtml\">online submission system</a>. See the <a href=\"/ijs/misc/ifora.shtml\">IJSEM Instructions for Authors</a> for more information regarding the layout and content of papers.</p>\n  <hr>\n  <h3><a name=\"VL\" id=\"VL\">Valid publication of bacterial names</a></h3>\n  <p>As required by the Bacteriological Code, the IJSEM publishes Validation Lists containing new names that were effectively published in other journals. For validation of new names published elsewhere, authors should submit a covering letter, a reprint (photocopy or PDF file) of the article(s) and copies of the culture collection certificates to the <a href=\"#EO\">IJSEM Editorial Office</a>. Requests can be submitted by email.</p>\n  <hr>\n  <h3>Publication dates</h3>\n  <p>The scheduled and actual publication dates for IJSEM and IJSB are available <a href=\"/ijs/misc/pubdates.shtml\">here</a>.</p>\n  <hr>\n  <h3><a name=\"EO\" id=\"EO\"></a><b>Editorial Office</b></h3>\n  <p>Permission requests should be sent to ijsem.permission @ sgm.ac.uk (please copy and remove spaces).</p>\n  <p>All other queries should be directed to Dr Karen Rowlett (Senior Staff Editor) at the Editorial Office.</p>\n  <p>IJSEM Editorial Office<br>\n  Society for General Microbiology<br>\n  Marlborough House<br>\n  Basingstoke Road<br>\n  Spencers Wood<br>\n  Reading RG7 1AG<br>\n  UK</p><b>e-mail:</b> ijsem @ sgm.ac.uk (please copy and remove spaces)<br>\n  <b>Tel:</b> +44 (0)118 988 1820<br>\n  <b>Fax:</b> +44 (0)118 988 1834<br>\n  <p>Last modified 3 December 2010</p>\n  <p></p>\n  <hr noshade=\"\" align=\"left\" width=\"450\">\n  <table cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"450\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HOME</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/help/\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">HELP</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/cgi/feedback\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">FEEDBACK</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/subscriptions\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SUBSCRIPTIONS</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/contents-by-date.0.shtml\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">ARCHIVE</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#003399\" nowrap=\"\">\n        <a target=\"_top\" style=\"text-decoration: none\" href=\"/ijs/search.dtl\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#FFFFFF\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">SEARCH</font></a>\n      </td>\n      <td width=\"75\" nowrap=\"\"></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody></table>\n  <table cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"2\" width=\"375\">\n    <tbody><tr>\n      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" bgcolor=\"#E1E1E1\" nowrap=\"\"><font size=\"-2\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"arial,helvetica\">INT J SYST